372
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,020
Ji Shu.

373
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:17,540
I've never let it go.

374
00:17:18,819 --> 00:17:19,460
I know

375
00:17:20,020 --> 00:17:21,060
