379
00:17:28,339 --> 00:17:29,020
Ji Shu.

380
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:31,260
Don't let me down.

381
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:33,700
Let bygones be bygones.

382
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:36,540
