386
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:45,460
I...

387
00:17:46,980 --> 00:17:48,500
We're just in touch at work.

388
00:17:49,260 --> 00:17:50,020
You hesitated.

389
00:17:50,500 --> 00:17:51,460
But do you know

390
00:17:51,780 --> 00:17:53,340
