521
00:23:52,060 --> 00:23:52,580
It's silver.

522
00:23:53,340 --> 00:23:54,100
This one?

523
00:23:54,940 --> 00:23:56,500
Yes, that's it.

524
00:23:57,500 --> 00:23:59,340
