877
00:41:31,700 --> 00:41:32,580
At that time,

878
00:41:32,700 --> 00:41:34,540
I was looking forward to seeing the sea.

879
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:36,100
But when I did,

880
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:38,540
